<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, August 23 (Xinhua) -- Brazil coach Wanderley
Luxemburgo has decided  not to take Romario to the Sydney
Olympics despite an intense media campaign for the veteran striker
's inclusion.
</P>
<P>
A statement issued by the Brazilian Football Confederation (CBF)
on Wednesday said: "Wanderley understands and respects the wishes
of the player but the decision made by the staff and the CBF is to
take only players under the age of 23.
</P>
