would have been among the favourites for his will and his quality
as a player."
</P>
<P>
The Olympic soccer tournament is limited to players under 23
but each team can field up to three over-age players.
</P>
<P>
Luxemburgo, coach of both Brazil's senior and Olympic teams,
announced his squad on Friday and said he had decided against
taking older players so that he could reward the squad who
qualified the country in the first place. 
