tourism activities including folk art performances, ethnic sports,
recreational programs, display of folk ceremonies, ethnic dance
shows and traditional snacks.
</P>
<P>
The event will bring to the public a panorama of traditional
folk customs from the country's Korean ethnic group, said a local
tourism official.
</P>
<P>
The traditional folk customs are as famous as its beautiful
landscape to tourists worldwide, the official said, adding that
the festival will introduce people to the cultural customs of the
ethnic group. 
