<P>
The earthquake also destroyed 3, 300 rooms, killed 59 animals,
and seriously damaged local water conservation facilities,
transportation, communication and other infrastructure, resulting
in more than 300 million yuan in economic losses, according to the
county magistrate.
</P>
<P>
Ten tons of rice and 300,000 yuan of capital were rushed to the
quake-hit areas. Rescue work is going on smoothly. No outbreaks of
epidemic has been reported, sources said.
</P>
<P>
An earthquake measuring 6.5 on the Richter scale jolted the
county in 1995. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
