trial will be conducted at the agriculture ministry building
instead of at the South Jakarta District Court building.
</P>
<P>
He said that the decision was made for the sake of security
reasons as predicted there will be a lot of spectators.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile many parties expected that the trial will be
televised to the nation in order that people around the country
could see the trial process. 
