In a statement, he said 75,000 A category tickets kept aside
from last year's disastrous original premium tickets programme
would go on sale to the public sale.
</P>
<P>
Knight noted that "They're some of the hottest tickets around
and we will sell them at list price."
</P>
<P>
The 75,000 tickets cover athletics, artistic gymnastics,
basketball and soccer. 
