<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 23 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
lost 13 Hong Kong dollars to close at 2,535 HK dollars a tael
Wednesday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold
dealers in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 273.04 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, down 1.43 U.S. dollar from the previous trading session at
Wednesday's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7935 HK
dollars. 
</P>
