this prisoner after receiving a full report from the security
forces and on the advice of the police this morning," said Britain
's Northern Ireland Secretary Peter Mandelson in a statement.
</P>
<P>
Adair's arrest followed days of violence in the Northern
Ireland capital of Belfast, triggered by feuding between rival
Protestant guerrilla groups. (UK-N.Ireland-Arrest)
