<HEADLINE> Pakistan Opposes Religious Militancy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 22 (Xinhua) -- The Pakistani present
government has effectively curbed the sectarian violence and
arrested all culprits involved in religious militancy.
